Package: esios2fd
Type: Package
Title: Download and Convert ESIOS Indicators to Functional Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Manuel", "Oviedo", email = "manuel.oviedo@udc.es", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides functions to download raw time-series indicators from the Spanish ESIOS API
    and to process them into functional data (fdata) objects and daily matrices (ldata).
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
